class_notes: EMPH Students Only; Outside permission to enroll in course must be approved by EMPH leadership. An additional session will be held on Saturday, January, from 4:30-6:30pm. EMPH Opening Weekend is 1/7-1/9 and Closing Weekend is 4/8-4/10.
course_description: Advanced Modeling will cover multivariate methods for analyzing epidemiologic data that involve examining associations between exposures and outcomes for which the outcome data are the time to an event, event rates, or a count of events. The course covers survival analysis and Poisson regression.
